data.description: Welcome Home to this 3 bedroom-2 Bath-2 Car Attached Garage with a basement located in a tiny community along Route 66.  Sitting on 5 lots with fenced backyard and a circular drive on a corner lot.  Ideal for someone wanting to send their kids to Adrian School or someone looking to live in a rural area.  Needs some TLC. Don't be afraid to make an offer!
